'''Kamano ya bojalwa le mogare wa HIV le bolwetse jwa AIDS'''<br />


Nnotagi e na le seabe mogo anameng ga mogare wa [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HIV HIV] le go kuketsa bolwetse jwa [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HIV/AIDS AIDS].
<br>
A o itse gore go dirisa nnotagi phetelela go ka go tsenya mo diphatseng tsa go tsenwa ke mogare wa [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HIV/AIDS HIV/AIDS]?<br />
Batho ba ba iphitisang nnotagi ba tshabelelwa ke tse di latelang:<br />
* Ba ka lebala go dirisa [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Condom Khondomo] kgotsa go sa e dirise sentle fa ba tlhakanela dikobo mogo ka felelang go baka boimana jo bo sa rulaganngwang, le gone go tsenwa ke malwetse a dikobo go akaretswa le mogare wa [http://%5B%5Bhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HIV|HIV%5D%5D HIV].<br />
* Go thubediwa ke batho ba le bantsi ka nako e le nngwa fela.<br />
* Go lebala go nwa melemo jaaka ya [http://%5B%5Bhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ARV|ARV%5D%5D ARV] ka nako le go sala ditaelo tsa ba bongaka morago.
* Go tsaya kgotsa go tseelwa dikobo ka dikgoka.<br />
<br />
''Se o ka se dirang go iphemela mo go tsenweng ke mogare morago ga maitiso a nnotagi:''<br />
* Ikgaphe mo go nweng phetelela mog go ka go tsenyang mo diphatseng tsa go diriswa botlhaswa, go tlhakanela dikobo osa itshireletsa kgotsa go tseelwa dikobo ka dikgoka.<br />
* Dirisa khondomo sentle nako tsotlhe fa o tlhakanela dikobo<br />
* Ikgaphe mo go tsamaeng o le nosi bosigo.<br />
* Ikgaphe mo go diriseng dipagamo tsa batho ba o sa ba itseng.<br />
<br />
''Fa o na le bothata ba nnotagi leletsa: BOSASNet (3959119), Women Against Rape (6860865), bodiredi jwa boipelego le mafelo a mangwa a tshidilo maikutlo, dikokelwana le dikokelo tse di gaufi.''

